statements: SELECT * FROM experimental_data;
SELECT experiment_date, temperature, pH FROM experimental_data WHERE bioreactor_id = 1;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_date FROM experimental_data ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT AVG(temperature), AVG(pH), AVG(oxygen_level) FROM experimental_data;
SELECT * FROM experimental_data WHERE temperature > 30 ORDER BY pH ASC;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_date, temperature FROM experimental_data WHERE temperature > 30 ORDER BY experiment_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM experimental_data WHERE bioreactor_id IN (1, 2, 3) ORDER BY PH ASC;
SELECT AVG(temperature), MAX(agitation_speed), MIN(oxygen_level) FROM experimental_data GROUP BY bioreactor_id HAVING AVG(temperature) > 25;
SELECT bioreactor_id, COUNT(*) AS total_experiments FROM experimental_data GROUP BY bioreactor_id ORDER BY total_experiments DESC;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_date, temperature, pH FROM experimental_data WHERE temperature < 25 AND pH > 7 ORDER BY experiment_date ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM bioprocessing_data WHERE experiment_type = 'Mixing'
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_date, measured_parameter FROM bioprocessing_data WHERE experiment_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY experiment_date DESC
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_type, parameter_value FROM bioprocessing_data WHERE parameter_value > 100 ORDER BY parameter_value ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quality_control_results WHERE pass_fail = true
SELECT * FROM quality_control_results WHERE analysis_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2023-01-01'
SELECT * FROM bioprocessing_data WHERE experiment_type = 'FERMENTATION';
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_date, measured_parameter FROM bioprocessing_data WHERE parameter_value > 1000;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_date, measured_parameter FROM bioprocessing_data ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM bioprocessing_data WHERE experiment_type = 'BIOREACTOR' AND measured_parameter = 'YIELD';

SELECT qc.result_id, qc.analysis_date, bd.experiment_type FROM quality_control_results qc JOIN bioprocessing_data bd ON qc.experiment_id = bd.experiment_id WHERE pass_fail = true ORDER BY qc.analysis_date ASC;
